sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title SEQ-3B: Update Calendar — Full HITL Flow (missing info, not found, conflict, edit, cancel)

    actor User
    participant MC as Message Channel
    participant BE as Backend API
    participant Agent as Agent Orchestrator
    participant LLM as LLM Provider
    participant TR as Tool Router
    participant Cal as Calendar Tool
    participant GCal as Google Calendar API
    participant ST as Storage / Memory

    User->>MC: "Dời họp Review mai"
    MC->>BE: Forward message
    BE-)ST: Async log raw message
    BE->>Agent: Forward request

    Agent->>ST: Load context + history
    ST-->>Agent: User context + recent conversations

    Agent->>LLM: Understand request + extract params
    LLM-->>Agent: intent=calendar.update,<br/>target=Review, date=tomorrow,<br/>missing=[new_time]

    Note over Agent: WRITE action → HIGH risk → HITL required

    %% === EDGE CASE 1: Thiếu thông tin ===
    rect rgb(255, 249, 230)
        Note over Agent,User: MISSING INFO
        Agent-->>BE: Hỏi params còn thiếu
        BE-->>MC: Reply
        MC-->>User: "Dời sang mấy giờ?"
        User->>MC: "10h sáng"
        MC->>BE: Forward
        BE->>Agent: Bổ sung: new_time=10:00

        Agent->>LLM: Re-extract với params đầy đủ
        LLM-->>Agent: All params OK
    end

    %% Tìm event
    Agent->>TR: search_events(title=Review, date=tomorrow)
    TR->>Cal: search_events(...)
    Cal->>GCal: events.list(q=Review, timeMin, timeMax)
    GCal-->>Cal: Matching events
    Cal-->>TR: Found events
    TR-->>Agent: Results

    %% === EDGE CASE 2: Không tìm thấy / nhiều events ===
    alt Không tìm thấy event
        Agent->>LLM: Thông báo không tìm thấy
        LLM-->>Agent: Error message
        Agent-->>BE: Response
        BE-->>MC: Reply
        MC-->>User: "Không tìm thấy cuộc họp Review ngày mai.<br/>Bạn kiểm tra lại tên hoặc ngày?"
        Note over Agent: Kết thúc

    else Tìm thấy nhiều events
        rect rgb(255, 249, 230)
            Note over Agent,User: DISAMBIGUATION
            Agent-->>BE: Danh sách events
            BE-->>MC: Reply
            MC-->>User: "Có 2 cuộc họp Review mai:<br/>1. Review Design 10h<br/>2. Review Sprint 14h<br/>Bạn muốn dời cái nào?"
            User->>MC: "Cái 2"
            MC->>BE: Forward
            BE->>Agent: Selected: Review Sprint (event_id)
        end
    end

    %% === EDGE CASE 3: Xung đột ===
    Agent->>TR: list_events(tomorrow, 10:00-11:00, attendees)
    TR->>Cal: list_events(...)
    Cal->>GCal: events.list(...)
    GCal-->>Cal: 1 event: "Standup 10:00-10:30"
    Cal-->>TR: Conflict found
    TR-->>Agent: Conflict

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Agent,User: CONFLICT
        Agent->>LLM: Tìm slot thay thế
        LLM-->>Agent: Suggest 11:00-12:00
        Agent-->>BE: Báo conflict + đề xuất
        BE-->>MC: Reply
        MC-->>User: "⚠️ 10h có Standup trùng.<br/>Đổi 11h-12h được không?"
        User->>MC: "OK 11h"
        MC->>BE: Forward
        BE->>Agent: Confirm new_time=11:00

        Agent->>TR: list_events(tomorrow, 11:00-12:00, attendees)
        TR->>Cal: list_events(...)
        Cal->>GCal: events.list(...)
        GCal-->>Cal: No events
        Cal-->>TR: No conflicts
        TR-->>Agent: Slot trống OK
    end

    %% === HITL GATE ===
    rect rgb(252, 228, 236)
        Note over Agent: HITL GATE
        Agent-)ST: Lưu pending_action
        Agent-->>BE: Preview
        BE-->>MC: Preview
        MC-->>User: "📅 Sửa lịch họp:<br/>Review Sprint: 14h → 11h mai<br/>👥 3 attendees giữ nguyên<br/><br/>✅ Xác nhận | ✏️ Sửa | ❌ Hủy"

        %% === EDGE CASE 4: User sửa ===
        alt ✏️ Sửa
            User->>MC: "Đổi thành 1 tiếng rưỡi<br/>và thêm chị Lan"
            MC->>BE: edit + instruction
            BE->>Agent: HITL edit

            Agent->>ST: Resolve "chị Lan" từ contact graph
            ST-->>Agent: lan@company.com

            Agent->>TR: list_events(tomorrow, 11:00-12:30, updated attendees)
            TR->>Cal: list_events(...)
            Cal->>GCal: events.list(...)
            GCal-->>Cal: No events
            Cal-->>TR: No conflicts
            TR-->>Agent: Slot OK

            Agent-)ST: Log edit request
            Agent-->>BE: Updated preview
            BE-->>MC: Preview mới
            MC-->>User: "📅 Review Sprint: 11h-12h30 mai<br/>👥 +chị Lan (4 attendees)<br/><br/>✅ Xác nhận | ✏️ Sửa | ❌ Hủy"

            User->>MC: ✅
            MC->>BE: approved
            BE->>Agent: HITL approved

        %% === EDGE CASE 5: User hủy ===
        else ❌ Hủy
            User->>MC: ❌
            MC->>BE: rejected
            BE->>Agent: HITL rejected

            Agent-)ST: Log rejection
            Agent->>LLM: Summarize cancellation
            LLM-->>Agent: Cancel message
            Agent-->>BE: Response
            BE-->>MC: Reply
            MC-->>User: "OK, giữ nguyên Review Sprint 14h mai."
            Note over Agent: Kết thúc — không execute
        end
    end

    %% Execute
    Agent->>TR: update_event(event_id, new_time, new_duration, new_attendees)
    TR->>Cal: update_event(...)
    Cal->>GCal: events.patch(event_id, body)
    GCal-->>Cal: Updated event
    Cal-->>TR: OK
    TR-->>Agent: Event updated

    Agent-)ST: Async log tool_call + HITL decision (redacted)

    Agent->>LLM: Summarize kết quả
    LLM-->>Agent: Confirmation

    Agent-)ST: Update session memory / audit metadata
    Agent-->>BE: Final response
    BE-->>MC: Reply
    MC-->>User: "✅ Đã dời Review Sprint sang 11h-12h30 mai.<br/>👥 4 attendees đã được cập nhật."
